Privacy Policy - JPJ Portal
Privacy Policy
1.
Privacy
If you make a transaction or send an e-mail containing personal information, this information may be shared with other government agencies to help provide a more efficient and effective services. For example in resolving a complaint that require escalation to other government agencies.
2.
Collecting and Operating Information
No personal information is gathered when you surf to these portal except for information given by you via e-mail.
3.
What Happens When I Link to Another Site?
This portal contains links to other websites. This privacy policy applies only to this website. It should be noted that other sites in the links may have different privacy policies and we highly recommend that you read and understand the privacy statements of each site.
